https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/150357#issuecomment-1541355074 - It seems that it's caused by `Web Annoyances Ultralist`.
@liaozipai please disable this filter list or add this rule:
```adblock
baidu.com#@$##head, .s_down, .s_form { position: relative !important; top: 0 !important; }
```
to user rules.

@wzxu That's all

